				"description": "# Close Order API\n\nThis endpoint is used to close an order in the system. It processes the request to finalize the order based on the provided parameters and returns a response indicating the success of the operation.\n\n## Request\n\n### Method\n\n`POST`\n\n### URL\n\n`{{dev_url}}/site/close_order`\n\n### Request Body\n\nThe request body should be in JSON format and include the following parameters:\n\n- **buyer_phone_number** (string): The phone number of the buyer associated with the order.\n    \n- **number** (string): The unique order number that identifies the order to be closed.\n    \n- **pay_system** (string): The payment system identifier used for the transaction.\n    \n- **buyer_uid** (string): A unique identifier for the buyer.\n    \n- **rrn** (number): The reference number for the transaction.\n    \n- **uid** (array of objects): A list of unique identifiers associated with the order. Each object in the array should have:\n    \n    - **uid** (string): A unique identifier for the specific item or transaction.\n        \n    - **discount_id** (string): An identifier for any discount applied to the order.\n        \n\n### Example Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"buyer_phone_number\": \"79119197189\",\n  \"number\": \"7116591\",\n  \"pay_system\": \"13\",\n  \"buyer_uid\": \"7b999e9b-34d8-4303-84a4-ec6681...\",\n  \"rrn\": 410921810829,\n  \"uid\": [\n    {\n      \"uid\": \"ef7dcf08-e6d7-47b8-851b-792b97...\",\n      \"discount_id\": \"ef7dcf08-e6d7-47b8-851b-792b97...\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Response\n\n### Status Code\n\n- **200 OK**: Indicates that the order has been successfully closed.\n    \n\n### Response Body\n\nThe response is in JSON format. If the request is successful, the content will be empty.\n\n### Example Response\n\n``` json\nnull\n\n ```\n\nThis endpoint is crucial for managing order states within the application, ensuring that orders can be effectively closed based on the provided identifiers and transaction details."
